body:
### Basic RPN Calculator App
I am following the ITunesU class on iOS App development by Paul Hegarty. He's an amazing professor. I just finished my first assignment of the class after watching couple of lectures. 

I want to share my experience on getting gitHub and xcode integration. It was a but struggle to update my Git and setup SSH keys to be able to push the code to the repository. I found a youtube tutorial very helpful to get this going.

[Setup Xcode with GitHub](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s7W7jyR0Uek)
